Question: Is the color of the pillow the same as that of the shuttle?

Reference Answer: Yes, both the pillow and the shuttle are blue.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n54424.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='pillow')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='shuttle')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What color is the pillow?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color is the shuttle?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == {ANSWER1} else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
